_sText:
A bigger, darker, and scarrier city map for ZM. The fog and lighting allows for a spooky atmosphere. There are three building to enter. Building Zero which has 2 floors + roof, Building One which has three floors + roof, and Building Two which has one floor. Theres a small park, car crashes, lots of fog, but dosen't effect your vision extremely, ally's and more!

Try it out.
